# Collection
- ClickEvent fields: timestamp, slug, ip_hash, ua_hash, referer?, country?, device_type?.
- No raw IPs by default; hashing with salt rotation policy.

# Retention
- ClickEvent raw: 90 days (configurable). Aggregates: 13 months.

# Subject Requests
- Provide deletion-by-slug and by owner_id for all raw events.

# Observability
- Structured logs (JSON); redact tokens and URLs with query secrets.
